WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.500 align:middle line:90%


00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:04.140 align:middle line:10%
A groundbreaking new
study of lucid dreaming

00:00:04.140 --> 00:00:07.080 align:middle line:10%
suggests that people can
heal psychological trauma

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:11.070 align:middle line:10%
while they're asleep and may
even show potential for healing

00:00:11.070 --> 00:00:13.470 align:middle line:10%
on the physical level.

00:00:13.470 --> 00:00:15.510 align:middle line:90%
This is Gaia News.

